{"tid":2347857,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"安排藝人吃炸雞被通訊局罰款　TVB司法覆核敗訴兼付訟費","createTime":"2020-12-31T10:35:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-31T11:09:08.000Z","uid":20933,"like":18,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8bb05f77c9c9a12352eb2f9300ce5818903d6605","tid":2347857,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T10:35:53.000Z","msg":"電視廣播有限公司2015年在一個頒獎典禮安排藝人食炸雞，以及於另一節目間接宣傳「myTV SUPER」，被指載入植入式廣告，分別遭通訊局罰款15萬元及警告，電視廣播不服處分提出司法覆核，2018年5月在高等法院開審，高等法院到今日頒下判詞，駁回電視廣播的司法覆核，認為通訊局的處分並無不妥，電視廣播要就案件支付訟費。 <br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2372967\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2372967&d=BLGvZshAgiFYydKSMDjJm3B8Xc4SSRTU1%2BC3UxNwN9M%3D&h=047839d5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2372967</a>"},{"pid":"c0e6e3c6b062616537744fca78b35188350b6a90","tid":2347857,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T10:38:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc56d7081e8d3dfcff9d4ed26b42500f2dcf7c0c","tid":2347857,"uid":36178,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T10:41:51.000Z","msg":"2015年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"168cd430e0ed251ae3cde28a7bed50570ec59c69","tid":2347857,"uid":302471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T10:43:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eeea72776e021b9299577b1f1a31ff5011b930f9","tid":2347857,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T10:44:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e63362f54c826445eaa1f2c8ebd281a04293b7ff","tid":2347857,"uid":76804,"like":1,"dislike"